 Kelly]], [[X Ambassadors]] & [[Bebe Rexha]] \u2013 Home \u2013 ''Bright''\n*[[Niall Horan]] \u2013 Finally Free \u2013 ''[[Smallfoot]]''\n* '''[[Selena Gomez]] \u2013 Back To You \u2013 ''[[13 Reasons Why]]'''''\n*[[Troye Sivan]] \u2013 Strawberries & Cigarettes \u2013  ''[[Love, Simon]]''\n\n===New Brazilian Artist===\n*Aretuza Lovi\n*[[Clau]]\n*[[Francinne (singer)|Francinne]]\n*J\u00e3o\n*[[Lu\u00edsa Sonza]]\n* '''Vitor Kley'''\n\n===New International Artist===\n*[[Billie Eilish]]\n*[[Era Istrefi]]<ref>{{Cite web|title= Nj\u00eb tjet\u00ebr sukses p\u00ebr Era Istrefin, arrin t\u00eb nominohet n\u00eb kompeticionin nd\u00ebrkomb\u00ebtar \"Break Tudo Awards\"|URL = https://telegrafi.com/nje-tjeter-sukses-per-era-istrefin-arrin-te-nominohet-ne-kompeticionin-nderkombetar-break-tudo-awards/|work=Telegrafi|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n*[[HRVY]]<ref>{{Cite web|title= Era Istrefi nominohet p\u00ebr \u00e7mimin nd\u00ebrkomb\u00ebtar \"BreakTudo Awards 2018\"|URL = http://fax.al/read/news/17563531/18802552/era-istrefi-nominohet-per-cmimin-nderkombetar-breaktudo-awards-2018|work=Fax|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Sigrid]]<ref>{{Cite web|title= Era Istrefi nominohet n\u00eb k\u00ebt\u00eb event nd\u00ebrkomb\u00ebtar muzikor|URL = http://www.gazetamonitor.com/era-istrefi-nominohet-ne-kete-event-nderkombetar-muzikor/|work=Gazeta Monitor|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n*[[SZA (singer)|SZA]]<ref name=sza>{{Cite web|title= Kat\u00ebr shqiptaret nominohen n\u00eb \"BreakTudo Awards\"|URL = http://rtv21.tv/kater-shqiptaret-nominohen-ne-breaktudo-awards/|work=RTV 21|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title= Era Istrefi nominohet p\u00ebr \u00e7mimet \"BreakTudo Awards 2018\"|URL = http://ata.gov.al/2018/09/11/era-istrefi-nominohet-per-cmimet-breaktudo-awards-2018/|work=Ata|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n* '''[[Why Don't We]]'''\n\n===Brazilian Viral Music===\n*Amor de Verdade \u2013 MC Kekel e MC Rita\n*Envolvimento \u2013 