the list of nominations with five mentions each. Anitta, BTS and Camila Cabello were the big winners, with four awards each.<ref>{{Cite web|title= BreakTudo Awards 2018 announces nominees including BTS, BLACKPINK, Cardi B, Taylor Swift, and more! |URL = https://www.kpopchannel.tv/breaktudo-awards-2018-nominees-including-bts-blackpink-cardi-b-taylor-swift-and-more/|work=Kpop Channel TV|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title= BreakTudo Awards 2018: BTS e BlackPink est\u00e3o entre os grupos de k-pop indicados, confira!|URL = https://www.clickparana.com/noticia/17976/breaktudo-awards-2018-bts-e-blackpink-estao-entre-os-grupos-de-k-pop-indicados-confira.html|work=Click Paran\u00e1|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title= Anitta: su primer \u00e1lbum discogr\u00e1fico gan\u00f3 un premio en los MTV Millennial Awards Brasil|URL = https://www.ciudad.com.ar/virales/anitta-primer-album-discografico-gano-premio-mtv-millennial-awards-brasil_102681|work=Ciudad Magazine|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title= BreakTudo Awards 2018 incluir\u00e1 3 categorias de k-pop na lista de indicados pela primeira vez|URL = http://revistakoreain.com.br/2018/06/breaktudo-awards-2018-incluira-3-categorias-de-k-pop-na-lista-de-indicados-pela-primeira-vez/|work=Revist Korean|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title= BTS, Jackson Wang, dan Mamamoo Menang BreakTudo Awards 2018 di Brazil|URL = https://www.jawapos.com/entertainment/25/10/2018/bts-jackson-wang-dan-mamamoo-menang-breaktudo-awards-2018-di-brazil|work=Jawa Pos|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title= BTS, Jackson Wang, dan Mamamoo Menang BreakTudo Awards 2018 di Brazil|URL= https://radarsemarang.com/2018/10/25/bts-jackson-wang-dan-mamamoo-menang-breaktudo-awards-2018-di-brazil/|work= Radar Marang|access-date= October 11, 2016|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181030205908/https://radarsemarang.com/2018/10/25/bts-jackson-wang-dan-mamamoo-menang-breaktudo-awards-2018-di-brazil/|archive-date= October 30, 2018|url-status= dead}}</ref>\n== Winners and nominees ==\n\nNominees were announced on August 25, 2018 through a post on the official website. The voting started on September 1 and closed on October 15. The singer Anitta leads the list of nominations with 5 nominations, one of them is for the category Best Fandom.<ref>{{Cite web|title= Nominasi Best International Group di BBC Radio 1 Teen Awards 2018, BTS Saingan The Chainsmokers \u2013 BreakTudo Awards|URL = http://bangka.tribunnews.com/2018/08/11/nominasi-best-international-group-di-bbc-radio-1-teen-awards-2018-bts-saingan-the-chainsmokers?page=2|work=Tribun News|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref> In the vice-leadership in the list of nominees, appear Demi Lovato, Camila Cabello, BTS, Cardi B and Taylor Swift. The winners were announced on October 21, 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|title= Brazil's BreakTudo Awards 2018 Adds 3 Categories for K-Pop After BTS\u2019 Wins|URL = https://www.kpopchannel.tv/brazil-breaktudo-awards-2018-adds-3-categories-for-k-pop-after-bts-wins/|work=Kpop Channel TV|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title= Anitta, BTS e Camila Cabello s\u00e3o os maiores vencedores do BreakTudo Awards 2018|URL = https://www.midiorama.com/anitta-bts-e-camila-cabello-sao-os-maiores-vencedores-do-breaktudo-awards-2018|work=Midiorama|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n\n===Female Brazilian Artist===\n* '''[[Anitta]] '''\n*[[Claudia Leitte]]<ref>{{Cite web|title= IVETE SANGALO \u00c9 INDICADA NO BREAKTUDO AWARDS 2018|URL = http://www.ivetesangalo.com/noticia-ver/ivete-sangalo-e-indicada-no-breaktudo-awards-2018-27082018|work=Ivete Sangalo|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Ivete Sangalo]]  \n*[[Iza (singer)|Iza]]\n*[[Joelma (singer)|Joelma]]\n*[[Ludmilla (singer)|Ludmilla]]\n\n===Male Brazilian Artist===\n*[[Alok]]\n* '''[[Luan Santana]]'''<ref>{{Cite web|title= Anitta lidera lista de indicados do BreakTudo Awards 2017 |URL = http://portalatualizei.com.br/noticias/anitta-lidera-lista-de-indicacoes-ao-breaktudo-awards-e-meus-premios-nick|work=Portal Atualizei|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Lucas Lucco]]\n*[[Leo Santana]]\n*Micael Borges\n*[[Thiago Brava]]\n\n===Female International Artist===\n*[[Ariana Grande]]\n*[[Cardi B]]\n* '''[[Camila Cabello]]'''\n*[[Demi Lovato]]\n*[[Selena Gomez]]\n*[[Taylor Swift]]\n\n===Male International Artist===\n*[[Bruno Mars]]\n*[[Charlie Puth]]\n*[[Drake (musician)|Drake]]\n*[[Ed Sheeran]]\n*[[Sam Smith (singer)|Sam Smith]]\n* '''[[Shawn Mendes]]'''<ref>{{Cite web|title= Shawn Mendes: sa tourn\u00e9e \"Illuminate World Tour\" est termin\u00e9e|URL = http://www.nrj.fr/artistes/shawn-mendes/actus/shawn-mendes-sa-tournee-illuminate-world-tour-est-terminee-353989|work=NRJ International|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n\n===Electronic Artist===\n*[[Avicii]]\n*[[Calvin Harris]]\n*[[David Guetta]]\n*[[Jonas Blue]]\n* '''[[Steve Aoki]]'''\n*[[Zedd]]\n\n===Latin Artist===\n* '''[[Anitta (singer)|Anitta]]'''\n*[[Becky G]]\n*[[J Balvin]]\n*[[Lali Esp\u00f3sito|Lali]]\n*[[Maluma (singer)|Maluma]]\n*[[Sebastian Yatra]]\n\n===K-pop Male Artist===\n*[[Baekhyun]]\n*[[G-Dragon]]\n*Holland\n* '''[[Jackson Wang]]'''\n*[[Jay Park]]\n*[[Taemin]]\n\n===K-pop Female Artist===\n*[[BoA]]\n*[[IU (singer)|IU]]\n*[[Hyuna]]\n*[[Heize]]\n*[[Bae Suzy|Suzy]]\n* '''[[Tiffany Hwang|Tiffany]]'''\n\n===K-pop Male Group===\n* '''[[BTS (band)|BTS]]'''\n*[[Exo (band)|EXO]]\n*[[GOT7]]\n*[[Monsta X]]\n*[[SHINee]]\n*[[Wanna One]]\n\n===K-pop Female Group===\n*[[Apink]]\n*[[BlackPink]]<ref>{{Cite web|title= BreakTudo Awards 2018: Anitta, BTS e BlackPink est\u00e3o entre os mais indicados|URL = http://www.ligacaoteen.com.br/entretenimento-variedade/breaktudo-awards-2018-anitta-bts-e-blackpink-estao-entre-os-mais-indicados/105539/|work=Liga\u00e7\u00e3o Teen|access-date= October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n* '''[[Mamamoo]]'''\n*[[Momoland]]\n*[[Red Velvet (band)|Red Velvet]]\n*[[Twice